    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一名痴呆症患者的祖父也曾因痴呆症备受幻觉的煎熬，跟着他拜访已故祖父的家，走进他杂乱无序的心灵。随着渐进性痴呆症将你的现实扭曲成陌生的模样，见证你感知的扭曲，重力失去控制力，空间和时间的本质融为一体，陷入一场诡秘莫测的舞蹈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超现实的家：</strong> 探索曾经熟悉，现在却笼罩在痴呆症的神秘之中的房子。穿越不符合物理原理的环境，在其中上和下都失去了意义，每个房间的布局错综复杂。这座房子共有18关供您探索。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>抽丝剥茧：</strong> 全神贯注地解决散布在神秘居所中的错综复杂的谜题。每个谜语都蕴藏着一段连接着记忆、梦想和现实的意义深远故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>记忆之旅：</strong> 当您更深入地探索不断变化的心灵空间时，见证记忆和虚幻的融合，体会清醒与幻觉之间界限的模糊。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>模棱两可的现实：</strong> 迎接不确定性。准备好质疑什么是真实的，什么是虚幻的，因为虚实之间的界限变得模糊了。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361510/extras/2368402e631a81c6c196ef5abda9468d.poster.avif?t=1763473745\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361510/extras/2368402e631a81c6c196ef5abda9468d.webm?t=1763473745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361510/extras/2368402e631a81c6c196ef5abda9468d.mp4?t=1763473745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>读档：</strong> 不再害怕过去的错误。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361510/extras/ccbf8fb2356da096ac075093d43fb288.poster.avif?t=1763473745\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361510/extras/ccbf8fb2356da096ac075093d43fb288.webm?t=1763473745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361510/extras/ccbf8fb2356da096ac075093d43fb288.mp4?t=1763473745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>准备好你的思绪，迎接一场幻想与真实的交响乐，让自己沉浸在旅程中，而这趟旅途和目的地都是一个谜。敢于走上违背理性的道路，拥抱饱受痴呆症折磨的心灵的无边境界。走进《Andarin Weppes: Pre-Dementia》的神秘世界，揭开在其中等待着的超现实真相。</p></li></ul>",
